This paper discusses the legal liability issues surrounding AI, which falls under the category of AI (cs.AI). It also touches upon the financial regulatory framework, which could be categorized under machine learning (cs.LG). The proposal of establishing an AI guarantee scheme involves legal and regulatory aspects, which could be classified under law (cs.LAW) and cybersecurity (cs.CR). Finally, the paper discusses the potential benefits of AI, which could be categorized under cybernetics (cs.CY).
